---
---
<section class="section about-section" id="about">
  <div class="container about-container">
    <div class="about-grid">
      <div class="about-info reveal">
        <h2 class="about-title">A Legacy of <span class="text-gradient">Excellence</span></h2>
        <div class="about-description">
          <p>
            Dr. Sharan Srinivasan is more than just a neurosurgeon; he is a beacon of hope for thousands. Graduating from the prestigious <strong>BMCRI (1992-1993)</strong>, he became the first student to pass DNB Neurosurgery from Karnataka in 2000.
          </p>
          <p>
            With a career spanning over two decades, he has mastered complex brain and spine surgeries, chairing sessions globally and bringing world-class expertise to India.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="about-highlights">
          <div class="highlight-item">
            <div class="highlight-icon">🏆</div>
            <div class="highlight-text">
              <strong>Sole Representative</strong>
              <p>AOSNR Managing Committee</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="highlight-item">
            <div class="highlight-icon">📍</div>
            <div class="highlight-text">
              <strong>Core Organizer</strong>
              <p>WCNR 2018 Mumbai</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="about-visual reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <div class="experience-card glass-card">
          <span class="exp-number">8k+</span>
          <span class="exp-label">Successful Surgeries</span>
          <div class="exp-progress">
             <div class="progress-bar"></div>
          </div>
          <p class="exp-subtext">Setting new benchmarks in neuro-surgical precision and patient care.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-section {
    background-color: var(--bg-slate);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 0.8fr;
    gap: 80px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .about-title {
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }

  .about-description p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .about-highlights {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 24px;
    margin-top: 40px;
  }

  .highlight-item {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .highlight-icon {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    background: white;
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    border-radius: 12px;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
  }

  .highlight-text strong {
    display: block;
    color: var(--text-main);
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  .highlight-text p {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .about-visual {
    position: relative;
  }

  .experience-card {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 60px 40px;
    background: white;
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    border: 1px solid rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.1);
  }

  .exp-number {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 5rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1;
    display: block;
    background: var(--premium-gradient);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .exp-label {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text-main);
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .exp-progress {
    width: 100%;
    height: 8px;
    background: #e2e8f0;
    border-radius: 100px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .progress-bar {
    width: 95%;
    height: 100%;
    background: var(--premium-gradient);
    border-radius: 100px;
  }

  .exp-subtext {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  @media (max-width: 992px) {
    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      text-align: center;
      gap: 60px;
    }
    .about-highlights {
      justify-items: center;
    }
    .highlight-item {
      text-align: left;
    }
  }
</style>
